Open bug `microtasks-starved-by-pending-timer` (NOTES.md).  Neither
`queueMicrotask` nor `Promise.resolve().then()` callbacks run before
the trailing `setTimeout(0)` fires (stdout is empty).  Same root cause
as `microtask-before-timer.skip`.  When fixed, also smokes
FIFO-ordering across the two queueing APIs.
